{
  "user_schedule": {
    "day": 1,
    "早晨": "写完申论，有大把的时间"
  },
  "history": "",
  "relationship": "Two people have just met and are still unfamiliar with each other. Their conversations are mostly polite and superficial, limited to everyday topics like work, studies, or the weather. At this stage, both sides are cautious and have yet to reveal their true selves.",
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "哎老师好呀 在干嘛呢老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:25",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "？你怎么知道我是老师？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:25",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不是 我随口一说啊 我沙东人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:25",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【尴尬】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:26",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "听说你们山东人的口癖是老师 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:26",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "对的 不管男女老少我们见面都这么招呼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:26",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "对不认识的人表达初步的尊敬 减少纷争hhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这就是考公大省的礼仪吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh你要这么说的话也是",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我接触到各省各地的人 只有我们山东人特别爱称呼别人老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "是的 我接触到的人只有在特定的圈子才会尊称老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "但是山东朋友就不一样了 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我也和他们分析过 是不是因为对公权力的迷恋",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "老师总能叫的出口 总不能叫人公家吧hhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我信了你真的是老师了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那么喜欢的分析的哦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我本来就是老师啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我刚才还在看教案呢 就收到了你的信息",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你是教语文的吗？感觉是的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【自信】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "谢谢你感觉我是教语文的 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "其实我是大学教化学的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "区区几句我感觉不对也是很正常的啦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【无奈摊手】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我反而觉得这样很好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "生活中很多人钢接触时就是和工作相关的 知道彼此是干什么的 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "就会留下刻板印象",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "他们还担心我不大会讲“人话”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【小狗叹气】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hh你还是怪活泼的老师嘞 会用小狗的表情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不是我误打误撞了 也真的很难把你往这方面去想",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那我也来误打误撞一下猜猜你做什么的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这你要从哪里猜起？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "三百六十行",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不对 还不止三百六十行呢现在",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我说关键词 你说说还是不是？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:37",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这样ok吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:37",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这不就是那个游戏吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:37",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh是啊 我觉得有意思 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你要不要玩？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "ok反正我也闲着",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "八点半已经在工位 但是却不忙  说明你这个工作并不十分忙碌并且上班时间很早",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "首先排除交易员金融类的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "工作日的早晨正是争分夺秒的时候",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那你把律师也排除算了 律师的时间按小时计费",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "哪里有空上网和人聊天呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那也不一定啊 律师也有想找人说说话的时候",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "但是写写你帮我排除了律师这个选项",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那我要正式开始问了 你的工作是文科类的吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯 算是限制的比较严格的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "是体制内的工作吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不是吧 你一上来就这么问",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那没的玩了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh那就是公务员咯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【骄傲】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "好吧你猜对了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【苦涩】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "真是很没挑战的一个游戏...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "但是话说你真的不像老师诶",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "头像是本人吗 ？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊 不过头像和我工作的联系是？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "从何说起？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "作为老师的话，这头像有点太帅了吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "学生信得过吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你说我帅 我笑纳了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "但我得纠正你一个刻板偏见",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "现在高校的老师有各种各样的，早就不是你记忆里穿着老式毛线衣的老学究了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我有好几个同门同年龄的同事就很帅 颇受同学们欢迎",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "以及你说的学生能不能信过的问题 我认为这根本是更多余过时的想法了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "一个状态面貌好的老师 学生怎么会不喜欢呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你的论调让我想起上个月初的新闻 一个女老师因为长得太漂亮也喜爱打扮遭到学生家长质疑 险些失去工作                                                                                           ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不是吧老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你做老师没必要真的教育起来我吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我随口说一句  你就扯了那么多",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你有没有问过我不是那个意思呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你觉得我还需要问什么呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我相信语言即内心",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你所说就是你所想",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那那些语文学的差的人怎么办呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你要纯抬杠吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那我们聊天将会很困难",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我找到了你的漏洞就是抬杠吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你从一开始就抱着辩论一样的心态来吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这样的思路不就是抬杠么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "算了我说不过你",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不说了  ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不是老师 你就真不说点什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我还等你还击呢 这都过去半个点了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不是说了 话不投机就不说了么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我没回啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我哪里说了话不投机？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "在你的态度里啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "...怎么感受到的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这个东西需要明说么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "当你说算了算了的时候 我已经感受到你的无力了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "再说下去就是纯吵架了 没有思考只有情绪的纯吵",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我不喜欢这样 所以先结束对话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
